    <div class="main-content">
        <h1 class="fw-bold">About - Healthcare System</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">This page provides detailed instructions and an overview of the different roles and functionalities available in the healthcare system for Admins Doctors and patients .</p>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <!-- Admin Panel Description -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card text-white p-4">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Admin Panel</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        The Admin Panel serves as the control center of the healthcare system, providing administrators with comprehensive tools to manage the entire system's workflow. Admins have the highest level of access and are responsible for overseeing all aspects of the system's operation, user roles, settings, and performance.
                    </p>
                    <h4>Key Features:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Manage user roles and permissions (Doctors, Patients, and other users).</li>
                        <li>Configure and adjust system settings for optimal healthcare delivery.</li>
                        <li>Generate detailed reports about system usage, patient data, and healthcare performance metrics.</li>
                        <li>Oversee patient records, prescriptions, and appointments across all roles.</li>
                        <li>Monitor system performance, including server health and data integrity.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>As an Admin, you will play a crucial role in ensuring the system runs efficiently by maintaining operational integrity and security. You will be responsible for adding, editing, and removing users from the system, and ensuring the smooth flow of medical data.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Doctor Panel Description -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card text-white p-4">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Doctor Panel</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        The Doctor Panel is designed to allow healthcare professionals to manage patient records, prescribe treatments, and monitor the health of patients over time. Doctors are able to review medical histories, update prescriptions, and work with other medical staff to provide optimal care for patients.
                    </p>
                    <h4>Key Features:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access and manage comprehensive patient medical histories, including previous treatments and diagnoses.</li>
                        <li>Prescribe medications and treatment plans, ensuring that patients receive the right care.</li>
                        <li>Schedule and monitor patient consultations and appointments.</li>
                        <li>Generate patient reports to track their progress and improve treatment outcomes.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>The Doctor Panel gives physicians the tools to ensure accurate diagnoses, maintain detailed patient records, and manage treatment protocols. Doctors can quickly access patient data and collaborate with the healthcare team to ensure the best possible care for every patient.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

